Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚纪念日呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.98,0:03:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到他有7个儿子
