Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.00,0:03:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一年的结婚生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明步 想拜托你件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.91,0:04:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
